;HYDROGENS HAVE BEEN ADDED IN THE RIDING POSITIONS CHAIN A AND B ARE CHIMERAS OF NDC80 (RESIDUES 80-286) AND SPC25 (RESIDUES 118-224). FOR CLARITY SPC25 RESIDUES ARE NUMBERED 1118-1224. RESIDUE 286 IS FUSED TO RESIDUE 1118 CHAIN C AND D ARE CHIMERAS OF NUF2 (RESIDUES 1- 169) AND SPC24 (RESIDUES 122-197). FOR CLARITY SPC24 RESIDUES ARE NUMBERED 1122-1197. RESIDUE 169 IS FUSED TO RESIDUE 1122 RESIDUES MET 79A, LYS 1122A, ILE 1161A, TRP 211B, ARG 1202B HAVE BEEN BUILT AS ALANINES BECAUSE THERE WAS NO ELECTRON DENSITY FOR THEIR SIDE CHAINS (SEE REMARK 470)
;
